const _wilderness_teams = {title: "Wilderness Teams", parent_topics: ["optional_subsystems","downtime","rooms_and_teams","teams"], siblings: ["wilderness_teams"], jsx: <><p><strong>Sources</strong> <Link to="/source/heroes_of_the_wild">Heroes of the Wild pg. 15</Link></p>
<p>These teams help wilderness outposts run smoothly.</p>
<div className="sideNoteWrap startAlign noIcon"><ScrollContainer id="rule-wilderness_teams--table-0"><table><tbody><tr><th colSpan={4} scope="col" className="title">Skirmishers</th></tr><tr><th scope="row">Earnings</th><td colSpan={3}>gp, Influence, or Labor +6</td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Create</th><td colSpan={3}>5 Goods, 4 Influence, 7 Labor (360 gp)</td></tr><tr><th id="rule-wilderness_teams-skirmishers-team-time">Time</th><td headers="rule-wilderness_teams-skirmishers-team-time">6 days</td><th id="rule-wilderness_teams-skirmishers-team-size">Size</th><td headers="rule-wilderness_teams-skirmishers-team-size">5 people</td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Upgrades From</th><td colSpan={3}><Link to="/misc/archers">Archers</Link>, <Link to="/misc/guards">Guards</Link>, <Link to="/misc/robbers">Robbers</Link>, <Link to="/misc/soldiers">Soldiers</Link></td></tr></tbody></table></ScrollContainer></div><p>Skirmishers are teams of archers and soldiers trained in the ambush, scouting, and stealth tactics necessary for operating in areas heavy with vegetation or other non-uniform terrain. They are typically 3rd-level warriors equipped with leather armor, a longbow or shortbow, and a handaxe or short sword. The team also has necessary equipment for travel in one type of wilderness environment.</p>
<div className="sideNoteWrap startAlign noIcon"><ScrollContainer id="rule-wilderness_teams--table-1"><table><tbody><tr><th colSpan={4} scope="col" className="title">Stewards</th></tr><tr><th scope="row">Earnings</th><td colSpan={3}>gp, Goods, or Labor +4</td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Create</th><td colSpan={3}>2 Goods, 2 Influence, 4 Labor (180 gp)</td></tr><tr><th id="rule-wilderness_teams-stewards-team-time">Time</th><td headers="rule-wilderness_teams-stewards-team-time">3 days</td><th id="rule-wilderness_teams-stewards-team-size">Size</th><td headers="rule-wilderness_teams-stewards-team-size">5 people</td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Upgrades From</th><td colSpan={3}><Link to="/misc/laborers">Laborers</Link></td></tr></tbody></table></ScrollContainer></div><p>Stewards are workers who specialize in caring for land with consideration for the local wildlife as well as any civilized inhabitants. Most stewards are 3rd-level experts with ranks in Knowledge (Nature), Perception, and Profession (gardener). Stewards may be trained professionals or common workers who have gained experience over time.</p>
</>};
